title: NJPW 52nd Anniversary Event & New Japan Cup 2024: Day 1
overview: NJPW 52nd Anniversary Event & New Japan Cup 2024: Night 1 was a professional wrestling event promoted by New Japan Pro Wrestling (NJPW). The event took place on March 6, 2024, in Tokyo at the Ota City General Gymnasium. It was broadcast on NJPW World.
